Let's play too.

295
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,000
Sure.

296
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:13,040
Come on.

297
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,080
Close your eyes when it's dark.

298
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:35,120
