299
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:39,480
Raise your hand if you have the same experience.

300
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:51,600
In our class,

301
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:54,960
22 students missed the toilet.

302
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:57,640
Put your hands down.

303
00:16:07,680 --> 00:16:10,920
She said she ran away from home.

304
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,680
Cool.

305
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:33,360
Five students are like you.

306
00:16:34,560 --> 00:16:36,320
Don't open your eyes. I'll catch you.

307
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:39,560
Put it down.

308
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:02,120
A student said

309
00:17:03,520 --> 00:17:06,920
