310
00:17:25,240 --> 00:17:28,400
One of our classmates had the same experience as you.

311
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:51,680
Eight students in our class pretended to be sick and applied for leave.

312
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,680
