One last question.

316
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:11,200
I hate this class.

317
00:18:17,800 --> 00:18:19,000
She said

318
00:18:20,080 --> 00:18:21,480
she hates this class.

319
00:18:45,320 --> 00:18:46,880
Only one student didn't raise her hand.

320
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:56,280
Open your eyes.

321
00:19:09,360 --> 00:19:11,080
I planned this game

322
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:13,240
