323
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:14,520
I guess you don't need to.

324
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:15,960
You two have a tacit understanding

325
00:19:19,720 --> 00:19:22,400
Ms. Song, why don't you sign up?

326
00:19:34,760 --> 00:19:36,240
It's not surprising

327
00:19:36,560 --> 00:19:37,680
In our class,

328
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:39,200
No class song, no uniform,

329
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:40,400
No one organizes activities.

330
00:19:40,760 --> 00:19:42,320
Everyone only cares about themselves.

331
00:19:43,080 --> 00:19:44,720
There's only competition between classmates.

332
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:47,120
If you all like such a group,

333
