334
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:54,520
Don't you look down on Class 18?

335
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:57,520
But honestly, it's not a coincidence that we lost the real shooting.

336
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:59,680
As long as it's a team competition,

337
00:19:59,800 --> 00:20:01,960
I'm sure you're no match for Class 18.

338
