360
00:20:53,960 --> 00:20:55,920
Do you know what I used to be the best?

361
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:56,680
What?

362
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:57,400
Short run.

363
00:20:57,760 --> 00:20:58,760
Short run.

364
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:01,840
Shouldn't it be a fight?

365
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,600
Nonsense!

366
00:21:05,520 --> 00:21:06,920
In my class,

367
00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:08,280
