377
00:21:28,560 --> 00:21:30,000
It's meaningful if you fail.

378
00:21:30,560 --> 00:21:32,360
At least you remember the second year of high school.

379
00:21:32,840 --> 00:21:34,600
There will be a group activity.

380
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:36,680
Maybe you won't

381
00:21:36,680 --> 00:21:38,280
