382
00:21:49,480 --> 00:21:50,440
Ms. Song

383
00:21:51,320 --> 00:21:53,440
Although it hurts today,

384
00:21:53,920 --> 00:21:54,880
I think at least

385
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:56,680
