400
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:09,680
Who knows who will be the head teacher next year?

401
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:11,200
Wu Yichen.

402
00:23:11,320 --> 00:23:13,360
Don’t you athletes usually train?

403
00:23:13,360 --> 00:23:14,600
