404
00:23:15,280 --> 00:23:17,720
I'm kidding. Many girls are watching the sports day.

405
00:23:18,040 --> 00:23:19,640
This is the most attractive time every year

406
00:23:20,840 --> 00:23:21,360
Okay.

407
00:23:21,360 --> 00:23:22,240
Stop pretending.

408
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:26,360
Women's record holder of 1,500 meters school

409
00:23:26,360 --> 00:23:28,120
Tan Shu Tong, 2014.

410
00:23:29,760 --> 00:23:30,880
Is that you, Shu Tong?

411
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:34,520
And 800 meters.

412
00:23:35,560 --> 00:23:36,600
You do sports, right?

413
00:23:36,840 --> 00:23:37,840
No.

414
00:23:38,280 --> 00:23:39,600
This is amazing.

415
00:23:39,600 --> 00:23:40,400
Amazing.

416
00:23:40,400 --> 00:23:41,880
How about you teach us how to run?

417
00:23:42,600 --> 00:23:44,720
I haven't practiced for a long time. I've degraded.

418
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:45,880
I didn't expect

419
00:23:45,880 --> 00:23:47,840
No one has broken this record.

420
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:50,520
Sam, I sign up for 800 meters.

421
00:23:50,720 --> 00:23:52,040
You won't run long, Qianqian.

422
00:23:53,080 --> 00:23:53,960
You are

423
00:23:54,120 --> 00:23:54,280
You are

