439
00:24:53,720 --> 00:24:54,640
You win

440
00:24:56,600 --> 00:24:57,680
Ms. Song is right

441
00:24:57,960 --> 00:24:59,560
I'll sign up for 1500 meters

442
00:24:59,960 --> 00:25:02,480
