474
00:27:57,760 --> 00:27:58,640
Stop pretending.

475
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:00,280
None of your business.

476
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:02,040
Waiter.

477
00:28:02,200 --> 00:28:02,920
Coming.

478
00:28:02,920 --> 00:28:03,720
Waiter.

479
00:28:03,800 --> 00:28:04,880
What's wrong?

480
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:07,080
