483
00:28:11,360 --> 00:28:12,120
Brothers,

484
00:28:12,200 --> 00:28:14,360
We give them as usual

485
00:28:14,360 --> 00:28:17,040
The meat in the rice roll is seasoned

486
00:28:17,040 --> 00:28:18,640
It doesn't taste good with too much

487
