491
00:28:26,600 --> 00:28:28,520
We do business with conscience.

492
00:28:28,520 --> 00:28:29,680
We won't miss you.

493
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:31,240
If you like it,

494
00:28:31,240 --> 00:28:32,360
I'll add some meat for you.

495
00:28:32,600 --> 00:28:35,560
