496
00:28:35,560 --> 00:28:37,480
it might not even cost enough for a plate of rice roll.

497
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:39,400
Please be considerate.

498
00:28:40,080 --> 00:28:40,880
Okay.

499
00:28:41,680 --> 00:28:42,600
I'll bring it to you right away.

500
00:28:55,360 --> 00:28:57,520
Here it is. It must be delicious this time.

501
00:28:57,880 --> 00:28:58,840
Try it.

502
00:28:59,480 --> 00:29:00,760
Okay, forget it.

503
00:29:01,720 --> 00:29:02,800
Thank you.

504
00:29:02,800 --> 00:29:04,120
Please come again.

505
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:10,800
9 yuan. Scan here.

506
00:29:11,040 --> 00:29:11,840
Only 9 yuan.

507
00:29:12,200 --> 00:29:13,320
What? You want more chicken soup?

508
00:29:13,760 --> 00:29:14,000
Okay, I'll give you ten. Chicken soup.

509
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:15,320
Okay, I'll give you ten.

510
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:18,320
10 yuan on WeChat.

511
00:29:18,560 --> 00:29:19,440
No.

512
00:29:19,440 --> 00:29:20,680
I'll give you a refund. Do it again.

513
00:29:22,080 --> 00:29:23,000
Hit me again.

514
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,080
I don't need your sympathy.

515
00:29:25,080 --> 00:29:26,680
It's not easy to pay if I collect too much.

516
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:28,520
Just promise me

517
00:29:28,520 --> 00:29:30,280
