521
00:30:00,080 --> 00:30:01,240
Just graduated.

522
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:03,120
Wesley, you know?

523
00:30:05,280 --> 00:30:06,400
The TV series

524
00:30:08,280 --> 00:30:10,640
Wesley is a famous American school

525
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:12,160
And she's an honorary graduate.

526
00:30:12,160 --> 00:30:13,480
I'm going to apply for a PhD in law.

527
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:14,720
Doctor.

528
00:30:15,320 --> 00:30:16,840
I want to be a human rights lawyer.

529
00:30:19,880 --> 00:30:21,920
Awesome, Dr. Lee.

530
00:30:23,840 --> 00:30:24,520
By the way,

531
00:30:24,520 --> 00:30:26,000
I'm looking forward to your sports day.

532
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:27,840
When? Can we watch it?

533
00:30:28,320 --> 00:30:29,480
Sure, next month.

534
00:30:29,920 --> 00:30:31,120
But don't get your hopes up.

535
00:30:31,120 --> 00:30:33,400
The students in our class do both hands and feet.

536
00:30:33,720 --> 00:30:35,760
They can even shoot under the basket.

537
00:30:35,880 --> 00:30:36,920
I seriously suspect

538
00:30:36,920 --> 00:30:38,840
