539
00:30:39,360 --> 00:30:40,840
If you can

540
00:30:40,840 --> 00:30:41,600
in your class,

541
00:30:41,600 --> 00:30:42,840
I really admire you.

542
00:30:52,760 --> 00:30:55,080
The four of you must be excited standing here.

543
00:30:55,520 --> 00:30:58,560
Because you're the best combination I've chosen.

544
00:31:00,480 --> 00:31:01,760
You have to believe one thing.

545
00:31:02,200 --> 00:31:04,800
I chose you not because there are only four boys in the class.

546
00:31:05,240 --> 00:31:07,800
