550
00:31:17,960 --> 00:31:19,280
Not bad.

551
00:31:20,560 --> 00:31:21,840
Don't you think

552
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:23,680
boys have less

553
00:31:24,120 --> 00:31:25,520
