554
00:31:25,760 --> 00:31:26,920
That's more than that.

555
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:28,280
There's no human rights.

556
00:31:29,120 --> 00:31:30,320
I knew it.

557
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:32,680
The man's life condition is still to be improved.

558
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:33,640
How to change?

559
00:31:34,080 --> 00:31:35,440
There are so many girls.

560
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:38,000
That's only part of the reason.

561
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:39,760
The most important thing is

562
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:41,920
