564
00:31:44,520 --> 00:31:45,840
Plus you are outnumbered

565
00:31:45,840 --> 00:31:47,000
That's why it's like this now.

566
00:31:50,320 --> 00:31:52,120
But now I have a solution

567
00:31:52,360 --> 00:31:54,000
